lead_paragraph: After mishandling Ray Rice's domestic violence incident two years ago, NFL Commissioner Roger Goodell said "I got it wrong" and vowed "the same mistakes can never be repeated."

headline.print_headline: NFL Didn't Learn Its Lesson After Ray Rice Incident
